                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18330103-113-off640 t18330103-113-cd641"></join>, 2 silver spoons, value 20s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18330103-113-victim1135" type="victimName">
